Title: 'The Gods Mistake Him '
DateModified: '2019-02-15'
DatePublished: '2019-02-15'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/the-gods-mistake-him
SetInCountry: Portugal
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Louis Elliott
AuthorCountry: United States of America
Text: She thinks she's going to meet a Jesuit priest to interview him for her dissertation.
  She meets a man in a cafe who turns out to be the priest. The Gods Mistake Him explores
  the lines of identity and obsession, mystery and reality. She must decide between
  professional ethics and personal liberation.
